  <brief_title>The Effects of TAP Block on Postsurgical Pain After Minimally Invasive Partial Nephrectomy:</brief_title>
  <official_title>The Effects of Ultrasound-guided Transversus Abdominis Plane Block on Acute and Chronic Postsurgical Pain After Robotic Partial Nephrectomy. A Prospective, Randomized, Clinical Trial</official_title>
  <sponsors>
